:60ad85f700001622  a    owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_1901976 ;
        rdfs:comment    "We determined differences in G1- to S-phase transition between wild type and ATF-2 m/m chondrocytes, a check-point specifically controlled by pRb. An increased number of cells had undergone DNA synthesis and incorporated BrdUin ATF-2 m/m chondrocytes as compared to wild type. The percentage of cells within the S-phase fraction ofthe cell cycle was increased in ATF-2 m/m cells. Theses results, taken together with the immunostaining for Ki67, indi-cate that ATF-2 loss results in aberrant cell cycle control mainly at the G1- to S-transition." ;
        layout:x        "1239.0504483821142" ;
        layout:y        "3614.387741942651" ;
        dc:contributor  "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3394-9805" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7476-6306" ;
        dc:date         "2025-12-03" ;
        pav:providedBy  "http://informatics.jax.org" .

